($$123 Mini Chefs at Best Start Family Hub: Queens Road$$, $$215 Queens Rd, London E17 8PJ$$, $$E17 8PJ$$, 51.576522, -0.027894799999999997, $$Developmental play$$, $$10:00$$, $$12:00$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=2976073963514090931&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/123-mini-chefs-best-start-family-hub-queens-road$$, null, null, 6, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Friday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-14; term time only. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$Enjoy the fun of cooking with your toddler, while transferring learnt skills from our class to your home. Age: 2 years and above This session is run term time only. Please note children attending this session must be able to use cutlery independently. Cost: £2.50 first child, 50p siblings. More information: Parental supervision required. Parents pay by debit card on the day using the QR code within the hub. We do not accept cash This is a Best Start in Life weekly session. When you see Curious Carina you can expect play and learning sessions that will support your child’s learning and development.$$, $$£2.50 first child, 50p siblings$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/123-mini-chefs-best-start-family-hub-queens-road$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2023-09/1-2-3%20mini%20chef.png.webp?itok=8V8urOdO$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/123-mini-chefs-best-start-family-hub-queens-road$$, $$ChIJ8QjxFb8ddkgRs9WLfIAjTSk$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=2976073963514090931&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 3.7, 6, $$health$$, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-17$$, $$2026-07-24$$, $$2026-07-31$$, $$2026-08-07$$, $$2026-08-14$$]::date[], null, null, array[$$Friday$$], $$specific_dates$$, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-14; term time only. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$published$$),
($$Baby and Toddler Clothes Exchange at Lea Bridge Library$$, $$Lea Bridge Rd, London E10 7HU$$, $$E10 7HU$$, 51.5707759, -0.0236276, $$Family activities$$, $$11:00$$, $$12:00$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=15028814885973325979&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/baby-and-toddler-clothes-exchange-lea-bridge-library$$, null, null, 108, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Friday$$], null, $$Council event on 2026-07-31. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$A baby and toddler clothes exchange day where you can meet other parents and exchange baby clothes for free. This is great opportunity to save money on clothes for your little one whilst getting to know other local families! 11am to 12pm on the last Friday of every month. This is a Best Start in Life session. When you see Active Ashton you can expect a session to promote your child’s health.$$, $$Free$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/baby-and-toddler-clothes-exchange-lea-bridge-library$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2024-08/116.png.webp?itok=xC-x28i3$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/baby-and-toddler-clothes-exchange-lea-bridge-library$$, $$ChIJd7ScnL0ddkgRm_iKQYMTkdA$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=15028814885973325979&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 4.1, 108, $$library$$, null, null, $$2026-07-31$$, array[$$2026-07-31$$]::date[], null, null, array[$$Friday$$], $$one_off$$, $$Council event on 2026-07-31. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$published$$),
($$Bambini's music and play (0 to1) at Queens Road$$, $$215 Queens Rd, London E17 8PJ$$, $$E17 8PJ$$, 51.576522, -0.027894799999999997, $$Music & singing$$, $$10:00$$, $$10:45$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=2976073963514090931&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/bambinis-music-and-play-0-to1-queens-road$$, null, null, 6, $$Under 2s$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Thursday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-13; term time only. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$Bambini’s Music and Play is a calming sensory session for babies aged under one year, featuring black-and-white visuals, mirror play, and tummy time to support early development. It encourages fine motor skills and engagement through singing, textures, and gentle interaction. This is a nurturing space for babies and carers to explore and bond. Age: Under 1s Cost: £2.50 first child, 50p siblings. Parental supervision required. Parents pay by debit card on the day using the QR code within the hub. Payment by card only. This is a Best Start in Life weekly session (term time only). When you see Curious Carina you can expect play and learning sessions that will support your child’s learning and development.$$, $$£2.50 first child, 50p siblings$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/bambinis-music-and-play-0-to1-queens-road$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2023-09/Spare%20-%20anything%20musical%20%28Carina%29.png.webp?itok=dqQqG9tS$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/bambinis-music-and-play-0-to1-queens-road$$, $$ChIJ8QjxFb8ddkgRs9WLfIAjTSk$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=2976073963514090931&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 3.7, 6, $$health$$, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-16$$, $$2026-07-23$$, $$2026-07-30$$, $$2026-08-06$$, $$2026-