($$Dad's Stay and Play at Wood Street Library$$, $$1, Troubridge Square, Wood St, London E17 3HB$$, $$E17 3HB$$, 51.5872756, -0.0038318999999999996, $$Stay & play$$, $$10:30$$, $$11:00$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=16001062556676665438&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/dads-stay-and-play-wood-street-library$$, null, null, 94, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Tuesday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-18. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$Come along to Wood Street library for our dad's stay and play session. A chance to meet other dads that attend the session and have a chat, whilst your children play. Every Tuesday Free event, suitable for ages under 5. For more information, you can message us on our Libraries Facebook , Libraries Instagram or email the libraries team .$$, $$Free$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/dads-stay-and-play-wood-street-library$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2024-04/Dads%27%20Stay%20and%20Play.jpg.webp?itok=lel3_Dfs$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/dads-stay-and-play-wood-street-library$$, $$ChIJ-9O8C_kddkgRXjCEN54xD94$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=16001062556676665438&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 4, 94, $$library$$, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-14$$, $$2026-07-21$$, $$2026-07-28$$, $$2026-08-04$$, $$2026-08-11$$, $$2026-08-18$$]::date[], null, null, array[$$Tuesday$$], $$specific_dates$$, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-18. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$published$$),
