($$Flourish (post-natal support group) at Best Start Family Hub: Chingford$$, $$5 Oaks Grove, London E4 6EY$$, $$E4 6EY$$, 51.625715199999995, 0.0096747, $$Feeding & postnatal support$$, $$10:00$$, $$12:00$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=9118098950548432754&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/flourish-post-natal-support-group-best-start-family-hub-chingford$$, null, null, 16, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Monday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-17; term time only. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$This session is invite only. A support group for mothers who are finding the transition into motherhood not to be as they expected. A chance to talk and share with other mothers feeling the same and learn to have fun with their baby. This session runs weekly, term time only. For more information call 0208 527 1737 or email familysupport@tlpcc.org.uk This is a Best Start in Life weekly session. When you see Brave Bilkis you can expect a session to help parents and children who may be having a difficult time. All sessions are run by skilled staff who are able to provide advice and information, and signpost to other family support services.$$, $$Check council event page$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/flourish-post-natal-support-group-best-start-family-hub-chingford$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2023-09/Flourish%2C%20post-natal%20%28Bilkis%29.png.webp?itok=1zefBnPY$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/flourish-post-natal-support-group-best-start-family-hub-chingford$$, $$ChIJq6reh5mg2EcRcidNjq_-iX4$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=9118098950548432754&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 4.4, 16, $$health$$, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-13$$, $$2026