($$HENRY infant feeding group at Queens Road$$, $$215 Queens Rd, London E17 8PJ$$, $$E17 8PJ$$, 51.576522, -0.027894799999999997, $$Feeding & postnatal support$$, $$09:30$$, $$11:00$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=2976073963514090931&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/henry-infant-feeding-group-queens-road$$, null, null, 6, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Monday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-17. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$Whether you are breast, bottle or mixed feeding, our trained HENRY infant feeding practitioners can help support you give your baby a great start in life. We encourage families to attend early on in the session to ensure the team can give you the support you need. You can also contact HENRY Infant Feeding Helpline (open Monday to Friday, 9am to 5pm) with any questions about feeding, before or after your baby arrives, on 020 7961 9073. This is a Best Start in Life session run by HENRY. When you see Active Ashton you can expect a session to promote your child’s health.$$, $$Check council event page$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/henry-infant-feeding-group-queens-road$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2023-10/Henry%20breastfeeding1.jpg.png.webp?itok=QvMQ-meC$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/henry-infant-feeding-group-queens-road$$, $$ChIJ8QjxFb8ddkgRs9WLfIAjTSk$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=2976073963514090931&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 3.7, 6, $$health$$, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-13$$, $$2026-07-20$$, $$2026-07-27$$, $$2026-08-03$$, $$2026-08-10$$, $$2026-08-17$$]::date[], null, null, array[$$Monday$$], $$specific_dates$$, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-17. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$published$$),
($$HENRY Infant Feeding Group Drop-in at Best start Family Hub: Walthamstow$$, $$313 Billet Rd, London E17 5PX$$, $$E17 5PX$$, 51.5983782, -0.0400823, $$Feeding & postnatal support$$, $$13:00$$, $$14:30$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=15753562951190599363&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/henry-infant-feeding-group-drop-best-start-family-hub-walthamstow$$, null, null, 2, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Tuesday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-18. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$Whether you are breast, bottle or mixed feeding, our trained infant feeding practitioners can support you to give your baby a great start in life. We offer practical and emotional support for all parents with feeding your baby at any stage. An opportunity to meet up with other mothers in a small group to get support on your infant feeding journey from a HENRY Infant Feeding Practitioner. If you feel your situation needs more time, please consider chatting to our team through the helpline before attending a session. Infant Feeding Helpline number is 0207 961 9073. This is a Best Start in Life session, provided by HENRY. When you see Active Ashton you can expect a session to promote your child’s health.$$, $$Check council event page$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/henry-infant-feeding-group-drop-best-start-family-hub-walthamstow$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2023-10/HENRY%20baby%20pic.jpg.png.webp?itok=8Twhk2Sb$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/henry-infant-feeding-group-drop-best-start-family-hub-walthamstow$$, $$ChIJVVWxdNYddkgRw1Z4xAnmn9o$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=15753562951190599363&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 3, 2, $$health$$, null, null, null, 