($$HENRY Women only infant feeding Café at Best Start Family Hub: Leytonstone$$, $$2-8 Cathall Rd, London E11 4LF$$, $$E11 4LF$$, 51.5581988, 0.0063729, $$Feeding & postnatal support$$, $$13:00$$, $$14:30$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=6357163216653723574&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/henry-women-only-infant-feeding-cafe-best-start-family-hub-leytonstone$$, null, null, 7, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Friday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-14. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$Whether you are breast, bottle, or mixed feeding, our trained infant feeding practitioners can support you to give your baby a great start in life. We offer practical and emotional support for all parents with feeding their baby at any stage. An opportunity to meet up with other mothers in a small group to get support on your infant feeding journey from an Infant Feeding Practitioner. To better support the families we serve, we have restructured some of our sessions. We strongly recommend contacting our helpline first on 0207 961 9073. , so we can direct you to the most suitable session for your needs. This is a weekly session. This is a Best Start in Life session. When you see Active Ashton you can expect a session to promote your child’s health.$$, $$Check council event page$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/henry-women-only-infant-feeding-cafe-best-start-family-hub-leytonstone$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2023-10/Henry%20breastfeeding1.jpg.png.webp?itok=QvMQ-meC$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/henry-women-only-infant-feeding-cafe-best-start-family-hub-leytonstone$$, $$ChIJz2n7tnin2EcRtifTi0MuOVg$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=6357163216653723574&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNl