($$Initial Sleep Consultation at Best Start Family Hub: Chingford$$, $$5 Oaks Grove, London E4 6EY$$, $$E4 6EY$$, 51.625715199999995, 0.0096747, $$Developmental play$$, $$15:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=9118098950548432754&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/initial-sleep-consultation-best-start-family-hub-chingford$$, null, null, 16, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Wednesday$$], null, $$Council event on 2026-07-15. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$Sleep deprivation not only affects a child’s learning, behaviour, mood and health but also the physical and mental wellbeing of the whole family. The Sleep Support team provide friendly advice for children over the age of one. For more information visit tlpcc.org.uk or call 0208 527 1737 or email: familysupport@tlpcc.org.uk . Sessions taking place 22 April, 20 May, 17 June 2026. This is a Best Start in Life session. When you see Active Ashton you can expect a session to promote your child’s health.$$, $$Check council event page$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/initial-sleep-consultation-best-start-family-hub-chingford$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2024-04/Sleepy%20baby%20%28Ashton%29.png.webp?itok=ARJP6pk_$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/initial-sleep-consultation-best-start-family-hub-chingford$$, $$ChIJq6reh5mg2EcRcidNjq_-iX4$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=9118098950548432754&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 4.4, 16, $$health$$, null, null, $$2026-07-15$$, array[$$2026-07-15$$]::date[], null, null, array[$$Wednesday$$], $$one_off$$, $$Council event on 2026-07-15. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$published$$),
