($$Kids Crafts at Walthamstow Library: Wednesday$$, $$High St, London E17 7JN$$, $$E17 7JN$$, 51.5843324, -0.021167000000000002, $$Arts & crafts$$, $$15:30$$, $$16:30$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=12456512494757751249&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/kids-crafts-walthamstow-library-wednesday$$, null, null, 252, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Wednesday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-12. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$Welcome to the Kids Craft Club, a world of imagination, creativity, and endless possibilities! Get ready to unleash your artistic talents and embark on exciting crafting adventures. Our club is all about nurturing young minds and encouraging self-expression through various hands-on craft activities. Suitable for children aged two and over, but little ones are welcome to be creative with support from their adults. Free admission For more information, you can message us on our Libraries Facebook and Libraries Instagram pages. You can also email the Libraries support team . This is a Best Start in Life weekly session. When you see Curious Carina you can expect play and learning sessions that will support your child’s learning and development.$$, $$Free$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/kids-crafts-walthamstow-library-wednesday$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2023-09/Kids%20crafts%20%28Carina%29.png.webp?itok=2rLoGM74$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/kids-crafts-walthamstow-library-wednesday$$, $$ChIJiZq9FPUNdkgR0SlA1h1s3qw$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=12456512494757751249&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 4.1, 252, $$library$$, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-15$$, $$2026-07-22$$, $$2026-07-29$$, $$2026-08-05$$, $$20