($$Play and learn (0 to 4 years) at Chingford Family Hub$$, $$5 Oaks Grove, London E4 6EY$$, $$E4 6EY$$, 51.625715199999995, 0.0096747, $$Stay & play$$, $$10:00$$, $$11:30$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=9118098950548432754&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/play-and-learn-0-4-years-chingford-family-hub$$, null, null, 16, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Tuesday$$, $$Friday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-18. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$These Stay and Play sessions are fun, interactive and informative run by early years professionals. They include a focus on the tip of the month on areas such as: Routines Imaginative Play Maths in books toys and games Movement and language Play and Language Environmental Print Musical Interactions Numbers everywhere Looking after me Mark making Talking and Listening Maths in everyday routines Food for Life Becoming a good listener Which will support your child’s learning at home. This is a Best Start in Life weekly session. When you see Curious Carina you can expect play and learning sessions that will support your child’s learning and development.$$, $$Check council event page$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/play-and-learn-0-4-years-chingford-family-hub$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2024-04/Play%20Session%20%28Carina%29.png.webp?itok=UwmiRvr-$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/play-and-learn-0-4-years-chingford-family-hub$$, $$ChIJq6reh5mg2EcRcidNjq_-iX4$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=9118098950548432754&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 4.4, 16, $$health$$, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-14$$, $$2026-07-17$$, $$2026-07-21$$, $$2026-07-24$$, $$2026-07-28$$, $$2026-07-31$$, $$2026-08-04$$, $$202