($$Play and learn for under 2's at Seddon centre, Leyton$$, $$Forest Community Centre, 33 Clyde Pl, London E10 5AS$$, $$E10 5AS$$, 51.570335899999996, -0.014966, $$Stay & play$$, $$13:00$$, $$14:30$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=2597480677822817114&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/play-and-learn-under-2s-seddon-centre-leyton$$, null, null, 5, $$Under 2s$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Monday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-17; term time only. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$These Stay and Play sessions are fun, interactive and informative, led by Early Years professionals. Each month, we focus on a different theme to help support your child's learning at home. Topics include: establishing daily habits through routines encouraging creativity making maths fun language and listening skills music movement and physical activity, and much more. Every session is thoughtfully designed to welcome all children, no matter their development stage or neurodiversity. At the end of the session you can take home ideas to support your child's development in a fun and engaging way! This is a Best Start in Life weekly session (term-time only). When you see Curious Carina you can expect play and learning sessions that will support your child’s learning and development.$$, $$Check council event page$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/play-and-learn-under-2s-seddon-centre-leyton$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2023-09/Under%202s%20play%20session%20%28Carina%29.png.webp?itok=Gt1dxQRI$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/play-and-learn-under-2s-seddon-centre-leyton$$, $$ChIJ58rgAZEddkgRWuORGOoaDCQ$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=2597480677822817114&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 3.8, 5, $$community_center$$, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-13$$, $$2026-07-20$$, $$2026-07-27$$, $$2026-08-03$$, $$2026-08-10$$, $$2026-08-17$$]::date[], null, null, array[$$Monday$$], $$specific_dates$$, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-17; term time only. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$published$$),
($$Play and learn for under-2s at Best Start Family Hub: Chingford$$, $$5 Oaks Grove, London E4 6EY$$, $$E4 6EY$$, 51.625715199999995, 0.0096747, $$Stay & play$$, $$10:00$$, $$11:30$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=9118098950548432754&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/play-and-learn-under-2s-best-start-family-hub-chingford$$, null, null, 16, $$Under 2s$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Friday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-14; term time only. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$These Stay and Play sessions are fun, interactive and informative run by early years professionals. They include a focus on the tip of the month on areas such as: routines imaginative Play maths in books toys and games movement and language play and Language environmental Print musical Interactions numbers everywhere looking after me mark making talking and Listening maths in everyday routines food for Life becoming a good listener Which will support your child’s learning at home. HENRY Healthy Eating and Dental Health Drop-in within Play Session on the second week of the month. This is a Best Start in Life weekly session, and no booking is required (term-time only). When you see Curious Carina you can expect play and learning sessions that will support your child’s learning and development.$$, $$Check council event page$$, true, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/play-and-learn-under-2s-best-start-family-hub-chingford$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2023-09/Under%202s%20play%20session%20%28Carina%29.png.webp?itok=Gt1dxQRI$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/play-and-learn-under-2s-best-start-family-hub-chingford$$, $$ChIJq6reh5mg2EcRcidNjq_-iX4$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=9118098950548432754&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEI