($$Quit Right at Best Start Family Hub: Chingford$$, $$5 Oaks Grove, London E4 6EY$$, $$E4 6EY$$, 51.625715199999995, 0.0096747, $$Family activities$$, $$15:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=9118098950548432754&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/quit-right-best-start-family-hub-chingford$$, null, null, 16, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Wednesday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-12. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$If you live, work, study or are registered with a GP in Waltham Forest, you can get free, confidential advice, information, and support to help you stop smoking. Quitting using QuitRight will greatly increase your chances of becoming smoke-free. Our specialist advisors can help find a treatment option that is right for you, making it even easier to quit smoking and beat the cravings. These sessions are appointment-only. To book an appointment with one of our QuitRight advisors, you can self-refer through QuitRight , or call 0800 169 1943. Find more information about the Quit smoking sessions. This is a Best Start in Life session. When you see Active Ashton you can expect a session to promote your child’s health.$$, $$Free$$, true, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/quit-right-best-start-family-hub-chingford$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2024-04/Quit%20Right%20%28Ashton%29.png.webp?itok=GwUAmx6C$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/quit-right-best-start-family-hub-chingford$$, $$ChIJq6reh5mg2EcRcidNjq_-iX4$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=9118098950548432754&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 4.4, 16, $$health$$, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-15$$, $$2026-07-22$$, $$2026-07-29$$, $$2026-08-05$$, $$2026-08-12$$]::date[], null, n