($$Quit Right Waltham Forest at Walthamstow Library$$, $$High St, London E17 7JN$$, $$E17 7JN$$, 51.5843324, -0.021167000000000002, $$Family activities$$, $$16:00$$, $$19:00$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=12456512494757751249&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/quit-right-waltham-forest-walthamstow-library$$, null, null, 252, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Tuesday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-18. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$If you live, work, study or are registered with a GP in Waltham Forest, you can get free, confidential advice, information, and support to help you stop smoking. Quitting using QuitRight will greatly increase your chances of becoming smoke-free. Our specialist advisors can help find a treatment option that is right for you, making it even easier to quit smoking and beat the cravings. You can self-refer through the QuitRight webpage , call 0207 882 8230 to book, or simply walk in. Find more information about the Quit smoking sessions. This is a Best Start in Life session. When you see Active Ashton you can expect a session to promote your child’s health.$$, $$Free$$, true, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/quit-right-waltham-forest-walthamstow-library$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2024-04/Quit%20Right%20%28Bilkis%29.png.webp?itok=Ch__U8E9$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/quit-right-waltham-forest-walthamstow-library$$, $$ChIJiZq9FPUNdkgR0SlA1h1s3qw$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=12456512494757751249&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 4.1, 252, $$library$$, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-14$$, $$2026-07-21$$, $$2026-07-28$$, $$2026-08-04$$, $$2026-08-11$$, $$2026-08-18$$]::date[], null, null, array[$$Tuesday$$], $$sp