($$The parents lounge: Break Tha Cycle, Queens Road$$, $$215 Queens Rd, London E17 8PJ$$, $$E17 8PJ$$, 51.576522, -0.027894799999999997, $$Family activities$$, $$13:00$$, $$15:00$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=2976073963514090931&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/parents-lounge-break-tha-cycle-queens-road$$, null, null, 6, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Tuesday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-18; term time only. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$A safe space for parents to discuss topics that affect them, to make new friends, and create a parent community. A space by parents for parents of under 5s. Weekly, term time only. Appointments by referral, or you can complete a self referral form on the day For more information, call 07535 280 467. This is a Best Start in Life session (term-time only). When you see Brave Bilkis you can expect a session aimed to parents and children who may be having a difficult time. All sessions are run by skilled staff who are able to provide advice and information, and signpost to other family support services.$$, $$Check council event page$$, true, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/parents-lounge-break-tha-cycle-queens-road$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2024-04/Break%20Tha%20Cycle%20%28Bilkis%29.png.webp?itok=-z72EE3S$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/parents-lounge-break-tha-cycle-queens-road$$, $$ChIJ8QjxFb8ddkgRs9WLfIAjTSk$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=2976073963514090931&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 3.7, 6, $$health$$, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-14$$, $$2026-07-21$$, $$2026-07-28$$, $$2026-08-04$$, $$2026-08-11$$, $$2026-08-18$$]::date[], null, null, array[$$Tuesday$$], $$specific_dates$$, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-18; term time only. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$published$$),
($$Under-2's Play Session at Best Start Family Hub: Leytonstone$$, $$2-8 Cathall Rd, London E11 4LF$$, $$E11 4LF$$, 51.5581988, 0.0063729, $$Stay & play$$, $$10:00$$, $$11:30$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=6357163216653723574&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/under-2s-play-session-best-start-family-hub-leytonstone$$, null, null, 7, $$Under 2s$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Thursday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-13. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$These Stay and Play sessions are fun, interactive and informative run by early years professionals. They include a focus on the tip of the month on areas such as: routines imaginative Play maths in books toys and games movement and language play and Language environmental Print musical Interactions numbers everywhere looking after me mark making talking and Listening maths in everyday routines food for Life becoming a good listener Which will support your child’s learning at home. This is a Best Start in Life weekly session. When you see Curious Carina you can expect play and learning sessions that will support your child’s learning and development.$$, $$Check council event page$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/under-2s-play-session-best-start-family-hub-leytonstone$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2023-09/Under%202s%20play%20session%20%28Carina%29.png.webp?itok=Gt1dxQRI$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/under-2s-play-session-best-start-family-hub-leytonstone$$, $$ChIJz2n7tnin2EcRtifTi0MuOVg$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=6357163216653723574&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 3.3, 7, $$health$$, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-16$$, $$2026-07-23$$, $$2026-07-30$$, $$2026-08-06$$, $$2026-08-13$$]::date[], null, null, array[$$Thursday$$], $$specific_dates$$, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-13. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$published$$),
($$Upcycled Kid's Craft at North Chingford Library$$, $$The Grn, London E4 7EN$$, $$E4 7EN$$, 51.6315088, 0.0028544, $$Arts & crafts$$, $$16:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=12294318940621743426&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/upcycled-kids-craft-north-chingford-library$$, null, null, 59, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Friday$$], null, $$Council event on 2026-08-07. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$We supply junk modelling resources, you supply your imagination and creativity! You are welcome to bring your own recycled items as well. This session is a lovely opportunity for children to collaborate imaginatively and creatively with their adults. Suitable for children 3+ For more information, you can message us on our Libraries Facebook or Libraries Instagram or send us an email here: Libraries.support@walthamforest.gov.uk$$, $$Check council event page$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/upcycled-kids-craft-north-chingford-library$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2025-05/upcycled%20kids%20craft%20image.jpg.webp?itok=Ug9-2_EP$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/upcycled-kids-craft-north-chingford-library$$, $$ChIJJ1FLX7cFdkgRQqUdO_Axnqo$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=12294318940621743426&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 3.9, 59, $$library$$, null, null, $$2026-08-07$$, array[$$2026-08-07$$]::date[], null, null, array[$$Friday$$], $$one_off$$, $$Council event on 2026-08-07. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$published$$),
($$You and Your New Baby at Best Start Family Hub: Chingford$$, $$5 Oaks Grove, London E4 6EY$$, $$E4 6EY$$, 51.625715199999995, 0.0096747, $$Feeding & postnatal support$$, $$13:30$$, $$15:00$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=9118098950548432754&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/you-and-your-new-baby-best-start-family-hub-chingford$$, null, null, 16, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Tuesday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-18. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$Your baby’s first social group! Have fun meeting other families with babies, share experiences and learn how to support your child’s development in a fun and relaxing environment. You can join in from pregnancy until your baby is crawling. Age range: Birth to pre-crawlers, antenatal and post-natal. This is a Best Start in Life session. When you see Curious Carina you can expect play and learning sessions that will support your child’s learning and development.$$, $$Check council event page$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/you-and-your-new-baby-best-start-family-hub-chingford$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2023-09/Spare%20-%20baby%20play%20%28Carina%29.png.webp?itok=9U58GtcG$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/you-and-your-new-baby-best-start-family-hub-chingford$$, $$ChIJq6reh5mg2EcRcidNjq_-iX4$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=9118098950548432754&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 4.4, 16, $$health$$, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-14$$, $$2026-07-21$$, $$2026-07-28$$, $$2026-08-04$$, $$2026-08-11$$, $$2026-08-18$$]::date[], null, null, array[$$Tuesday$$], $$specific_dates$$, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-18. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$published$$),
($$You and Your New Baby at Best Start Family Hub: Leytonstone$$, $$2-8 Cathall Rd, London E11 4LF$$, $$E11 4LF$$, 51.5581988, 0.0063729, $$Developmental play$$, $$10:00$$, $$11:30$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=6357163216653723574&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/you-and-your-new-baby-best-start-family-hub-leytonstone$$, null, null, 7, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Tuesday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-18. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$Delivered by The Lloyds Park Children's Charity Baby’s first social group! Come and have fun meeting other families with babies and share experiences and learn how to support your child’s development in a fun and relaxing environment. This is a Best Start in Life weekly session. When you see Curious Carina you can expect play and learning sessions that will support your child’s learning and development.$$, $$Check council event page$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/you-and-your-new-baby-best-start-family-hub-leytonstone$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2023-09/You%20and%20Your%20New%20Baby%20%28Carina%29.png.webp?itok=7HJxe5AL$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/you-and-your-new-baby-best-start-family-hub-leytonstone$$, $$ChIJz2n7tnin2EcRtifTi0MuOVg$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=6357163216653723574&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 3.3, 7, $$health$$, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-14$$, $$2026-07-21$$, $$2026-07-28$$, $$2026-08-04$$, $$2026-08-11$$, $$2026-08-18$$]::date[], null, null, array[$$Tuesday$$], $$specific_dates$$, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-18. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$published$$),
($$You and your new baby at Best Start Family Hub: Walthamstow$$, $$313 Billet Rd, London E17 5PX$$, $$E17 5PX$$, 51.5983782, -0.0400823, $$Feeding & postnatal support$$, $$11:15$$, $$12:45$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=15753562951190599363&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/you-and-your-new-baby-best-start-family-hub-walthamstow$$, null, null, 2, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Thursday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-13. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$Baby’s first social group! Come and have fun meeting other families with babies and share experiences and learn how to support your child’s development in a fun and relaxing environment. This session is for babies, pre-crawlers, antenatal, and postnatal delivered by The Lloyd Park Children's Charity. More information: HENRY Healthy Eating and Dental Health Drop-In within session on last week of the month. This is a Best Start in Life weekly session. When you see Curious Carina you can expect play and learning sessions that will support your child’s learning and development.$$, $$Check council event page$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/you-and-your-new-baby-best-start-family-hub-walthamstow$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2023-09/You%20and%20Your%20New%20Baby%20%28Carina%29.png.webp?itok=7HJxe5AL$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/you-and-your-new-baby-best-start-family-hub-walthamstow$$, $$ChIJVVWxdNYddkgRw1Z4xAnmn9o$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=15753562951190599363&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, 3, 2, $$health$$, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-16$$, $$2026-07-23$$, $$2026-07-30$$, $$2026-08-06$$, $$2026-08-13$$]::date[], null, null, array[$$Thursday$$], $$specific_dates$$, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-13. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$published$$),
($$You and your new baby: Stay and play at Leyton Sports Ground$$, $$Leyton Sports Ground, 485 High Rd, London E10 6PY$$, $$E10 6PY$$, 51.5672638, -0.0106515, $$Stay & play$$, $$10:00$$, $$11:30$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=17253523719233353505&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/you-and-your-new-baby-stay-and-play-leyton-sports-ground$$, null, null, 0, $$Parents, babies and young children$$, $$Waltham Forest$$, array[$$Tuesday$$], null, $$Council dates listed through 2026-08-18. Check the council event page for changes.$$, $$Join other families with little ones to share stories, make new friends, and discover fun ways to support your baby's development. Whether you're expecting or your baby is already on the move, this is a relaxed and friendly space to connect, learn, and grow together. These sessions are delivered by The Lloyds Park Children's charity. Open to parents from pregnancy until your baby starts crawling. This is a Best Start in Life weekly session. When you see Curious Carina you can expect play and learning sessions that will support your child’s learning and development.$$, $$Check council event page$$, false, $$Waltham Forest Best Start in Life events$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/you-and-your-new-baby-stay-and-play-leyton-sports-ground$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/sites/default/files/styles/3_2_lossless_responsive/public/2023-09/You%20and%20Your%20New%20Baby%20%28Carina%29.png.webp?itok=7HJxe5AL$$, $$https://www.walthamforest.gov.uk/events/you-and-your-new-baby-stay-and-play-leyton-sports-ground$$, $$ChIJRxBlWYUddkgRITeu2GjUcO8$$, $$https://maps.google.com/?cid=17253523719233353505&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA$$, null, null, 0, null, null, null, null, array[$$2026-07-14$$, $$2026-07-21$$, $$2026-07-28$$, $$2026-08-04$$, $$2026-08-11$$, $$2026-08-18$$]::date[], null, null, array[$$Tuesday$$], $$specific_d